Fair-Use Notice — Vegeta (Dragon Ball Z) OpenPeon Sound Pack

This pack is a non-commercial fan work distributed under a claim of fair use.

The audio clips contained in the `sounds/` directory are short excerpts of
voice lines from *Dragon Ball Z* / *Dragon Ball Super*, © Toei Animation /
Funimation / their respective rights holders. The English dub voice of Vegeta
is performed by Christopher Sabat.

These excerpts are included here solely for:

  - non-commercial, personal, fan/hobbyist use, and
  - a transformative purpose (brief audio notifications for AI coding agents),

using only the short portions necessary for that purpose.

No ownership of or copyright over the audio clips is claimed by this pack or
its author, and the clips are not relicensed. This project is not affiliated
with, sponsored by, or endorsed by the rights holders.

The manifest (`openpeon.json`), documentation, and structure of this pack were
assembled by Alex Lupu (https://github.com/alexlupu3) and are offered freely
for non-commercial use.

If you are a rights holder and would like a clip removed, please open an issue
on the repository and it will be taken down.
